data.description: Welcome to your opportunity to own a two-story gem with incredible potential! This as-is home boasts abundant space and endless possibilities. With two distinct living spaces, this residence offers the best of both worlds. This home accommodates all stages of life with two downstairs bedrooms, a full bath, and a convenient half bath adjacent to the laundry room. Downstairs, features a formal living space, formal dining room with ample storage and an office with a cozy sitting area. The spacious kitchen is complete with double ovens, an electric range, and a cooktop, built in microwave, trash compactor, dishwasher & pantry.  Upstairs features a large stone fireplace, a second living area, gameroom, primary bedroom with a suite, an additional bedroom & full bath.  Conveniently located minutes away from Texas A&M University, Naval Air Station & the Oso Beach Municipal Golf Course. Great Location with tons of potential.
